    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it\u2019s been meticulously maintained. Not a single scratch or dent to be found! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Swing by and see it for yourself!",
