    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. Riding on a refined suspension with Bilstein dampers and fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, the lateral dynamics are razor-sharp. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this is a turn-key collector's piece with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
