    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, original luster with absolutely no swirls, chips, or road imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium upholstery remains supple with zero bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive folder of service records from authorized technicians. The engine bay is pristine, reflecting the same level of care as the rest of the vehicle. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 48500.0,
